subject: Golf
Women's British Open (Golf)
lead_paragraph: Winning the 2010 British Open at Royal Birkdale helped catapult Yani Tseng of Taiwan to 109 consecutive weeks as the world’s top-ranked female golfer. She returns Thursday ranked No. 48 in the world.
